Вакансія від 23 березня 2020
Equity Analyst
Competative
St Charles Homes ltd
Будівництво;
менше 10 співробітників
Київ, вулиця Бульварно-Кудрявська, 26.
1,9 км від центру ·
На мапі
Повна зайнятість, неповна зайнятість.
Досвід роботи від 5 років.
Опис вакансії
Equity Investment AnalystWe are looking for an analyst to assist in building and maintaining an equity portfolio.Key Responsibilities:
Development of investment ideas for a Long-Short, market neutral equities book
Create and maintain business models to forecast business financial performance
Create and maintain business models to forecast business financial performance
Regular report writing to present investment thesis and rationale behind target prices
Analyse emerging economic, macro economic and industry trends to develop original insight as part of these responsibilities
Ideal candidate will have:
Excellent command of the English language.
3−5 years experience working with financial services institutions
Qualified ACA, (M&A, corporate finance, audit or transaction service divisions) or CFA Finance Masters or MBA are highly desired
Excellent accounting knowledge with the ability to Analyse balance sheets and cash flow statements
Excellent Technical capabilities with the ability to write your own models
Excellent oral and written communication skills are essential
NOTE: Please do not apply to this position if you do not meet the above criteria.Please apply with a CV and covering letter in English.
